---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const title = "Produk Pertanian";
const description = "Katalog produk Toko Tani Green Al Fatih: herbisida Asxone 138 SL, fungisida Copcide 77 WP, pupuk, insektisida, dan kebutuhan tani lengkap.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="py-16 px-4 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Produk Kami</h1>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-500 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Semua produk berkualitas untuk kebutuhan pertanian Anda. Harga bersaing, pengiriman seluruh Kalimantan.</p>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white border rounded-xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-4">
          <img src="/images/jual-asxone-138-SL-pangkalan-banteng-1024x576.webp" alt="Asxone 138 SL" class="w-full md:w-48 rounded-xl object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Asxone 138 SL</h2>
            <span class="inline-block bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-3">Best Seller</span>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Herbisida sistemik berkualitas tinggi untuk mengendalikan gulma berdaun lebar pada tanaman padi, jagung, kelapa sawit, dan tanaman perkebunan lainnya.</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1 mb-6">
              <li>✅ Bahan aktif berkualitas</li>
              <li>✅ Efektif untuk gulma resisten</li>
              <li>✅ Tersedia berbagai ukuran kemasan</li>
              <li>✅ Harga grosir tersedia</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://wa.me/6285251988382?text=Halo%2C%20saya%20mau%20tanya%20harga%20Asxone%20138%20SL" class="inline-block bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium transition text-sm">
              💬 Tanya Harga Asxone
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border rounded-xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-4">
          <img src="/images/jual-asxone-138-SL-Kalimantan-tengah-toko-tani-green-al-fatih-585x1024.webp" alt="Asxone Kalimantan Tengah" class="w-full md:w-48 rounded-xl object-cover" loading="lazy" />
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Copcide 77 WP</h2>
            <span class="inline-block bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-3">Fungisida</span>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Fungisida protektif berbentuk tepung yang dapat disuspensikan. Efektif mengendalikan penyakit pada tanaman cabai, jeruk, kakao, dan padi.</p>
            <ul class="text-sm text-gray-500 space-y-1 mb-6">
              <li>✅ Formula 77% bahan aktif</li>
              <li>✅ Proteksi tahan lama</li>
              <li>✅ Cocok untuk berbagai tanaman</li>
              <li>✅ Mudah diaplikasikan</li>
            </ul>
            <a href="https://wa.me/6285251988382?text=Halo%2C%20saya%20mau%20tanya%20harga%20Copcide%2077%20WP" class="inline-block bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium transition text-sm">
              💬 Tanya Harga Copcide
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border rounded-xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="text-5xl">🌱</div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Pupuk Lengkap</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Pupuk organik dan anorganik untuk semua jenis tanaman. Tersedia pupuk NPK, urea, SP-36, KCl, dan pupuk organik cair.</p>
            <a href="https://wa.me/6285251988382?text=Halo%2C%20saya%20mau%20tanya%20harga%20pupuk" class="inline-block bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium transition text-sm">
              💬 Tanya Harga Pupuk
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white border rounded-xl p-8 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="text-5xl">🐛</div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">Insektisida</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Insektisida sistemik dan kontak untuk mengendalikan hama wereng, penggerek batang, ulat, dan hama tanaman lainnya.</p>
            <a href="https://wa.me/6285251988382?text=Halo%2C%20saya%20mau%20tanya%20harga%20insektisida" class="inline-block bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium transition text-sm">
              💬 Tanya Harga Insektisida
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center bg-green-50 rounded-2xl p-8">
      <p class="text-lg mb-3">🤝 Butuh produk lain atau harga grosir?</p>
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-4">Hubungi kami langsung — kami siap bantu kebutuhan pertanian Anda.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/6285251988382" class="inline-block bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold transition">
        💬 Chat WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
